snippet.textDisplay: Meh. Great lyrics but very substandard to be a MTV Coke Studio song. With access to probably the best producers and musicians in the country, Coke Studio should be about presenting the Indian folk/traditional/classical music and folklores by giving it a more contemporary treatment like Amit Trivedi, Karsh Kale, Hitesh Soni, Clinton etc have done. This is just another attempt at writing an alternative rock Bollywood song.
snippet.textOriginal: Meh. Great lyrics but very substandard to be a MTV Coke Studio song.
